title: Google Dominating Search Ads More Than Ever
itunes:title: Google Dominating Search Ads More Than Ever
description:
Bloomberg News Technology Reporter Mark Bergen and Bloomberg News Senior Writer Shelly Banjo write, "the company’s push into health care is a case study in how tech giants dominate small businesses. And the U.S. government may have something to say about that."

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
